aradığım aşk değil.  

00:22:36.410 --> 00:22:42.460
watashiga motometeiru  
monotowa chigau  

00:22:43.050 --> 00:22:46.420
Eğer beyaz dersen,  

00:22:43.050 --> 00:22:46.420
shiroto iwaretara  

00:22:46.420 --> 00:22:49.890
ben siyah derim.  

00:22:46.420 --> 00:22:49.890
kurodatte icchau  

00:22:49.890 --> 00:22:53.350
Küçük bir şeytan  

00:22:49.890 --> 00:22:53.350
sunaoni narenai  

00:22:53.350 --> 00:22:55.850
kendine karşı dürüst olamayan.  

